---
title: Japanese Salmon Rice Bowl with Avocado & Wasabi Mayo
description: All the flavour of a sushi roll but all loaded into a wholesome bowl - from the tasty rice, succulent salmon, sauteed greens and creamy avocado, all topped off with a generous drizzle of warming wasabi mayo (if you like it!)
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/5b70fe2d30006c49a0318654-b772f7f1.jpg
